            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Root cause is in the shared `ex_listdo()` code - `:windo`/`:tabdo` unnecessarily\nescape a 'winfixbuf' window by splitting, even though they don't change the\ncurrent window's buffer. Same root cause as vim/vim#14301.\n\nI'm fixing it upstream in Vim first: vim/vim#20600.\nThat PR covers both this `:tabdo` case and the `:windo` case from vim/vim#14301.\n\nOnce it merges I'll bring it to Neovim as a `vim-patch:` port.",
